Late Nite Westside Inbound

Description:

The Late Nite Westside Inbound leaves Downtown Binghamton - State & Hawley Streets and travels through Main Street in Binghamton and Floral Avenue in Johnson City enroute to campus.


Reminder: All Late Nite buses at State & Hawley Street return to campus.

Operation Time:

Friday and Saturday:
12:00 A.M. to 2:50 A.M., unless otherwise posted.
